@baseUrl = https://scisure.atlassian.net
@auth = Basic {{$dotenv JIRA_EMAIL}}:{{$dotenv JIRA_API_TOKEN}}

###
POST {{baseUrl}}/rest/api/3/search/jql
Authorization: {{auth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jql": "issuekey in (ELAB-18161,ELAB-19363)",
  "maxResults": 100,
  "fields": ["summary", "parent", "status", "assignee", "priority", "issuetype", "created", "updated", "comment", "subtasks", "parent.issuetype"]
}

### 2. Search issues (classic endpoint — /search POST)
POST {{baseUrl}}/rest/api/3/search
Authorization: {{auth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jql": "issuekey in (ELAB-18161,ELAB-19363)",
  "maxResults": 100,
  "fields": ["summary", "parent", "status", "assignee", "priority", "issuetype", "created", "updated", "comment", "subtasks", "parent.issuetype"]
}

### 3. Get single issue directly
GET {{baseUrl}}/rest/api/3/issue/ELAB-18161?fields=summary,status
Authorization: {{auth}}
Content-Type: application/json
